    "en": {
      "title": "18 people were injured in the bus accident",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "18 people were injured when a private bus traveling from Udapussalai to Batticaloa veered off the road and crashed.",
        "The accident took place today (30) at 1030 am in Valappanai-Mahawa area.",
        "Those who attended a wedding event held in Udapullawai from Batticaloa and returned to Batticaloa have faced this accident."
      ],
